{"tid":472322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港獨思潮，我們需要你的參與！","createTime":"2017-11-18T06:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T04:52:36.000Z","uid":28366,"like":40,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2e424433be2af7cc730d905311cc75833c8a2635","tid":472322,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/23559737_1997467700494930_1399097278082332388_n.jpg?oh=f6bc37ae786c645ceafdd6f3258e3b30&amp;oe=5AA7B42D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F23559737_1997467700494930_1399097278082332388_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df6bc37ae786c645ceafdd6f3258e3b30%26oe%3D5AA7B42D&h=415f6a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【You will never walk alone】</span><br />\n在較早前的校園播獨行動中，多間不同地區，不同程度的院校成功連成一線，廣泛進行播獨工作，不少同學亦向我們反映校內同學反應熱烈，播獨行動已取得顯著效果。<br />\n<br />\n然而，宣傳港獨需要長時間的耕耘，並不是一朝一夕就能完成的事，在未來我們會繼續發動包括學界在內不同途徑的宣傳，在這條為香港人開創新天的征途上，我們需要每一個人、每一個關注組的參與！<br />\n<br />\n有志投身播獨事業，而又不知從何入手，或是缺乏支援無從做起，甚至屢受打壓被逼噤聲的學界同道們，當你看到這則訊息，請即聯絡我們。只有團結一致，我們才能力抗各方面的打壓，為自己，為港人重奪未來！<br />\n<br />\n本組織亦會於以下平台發送消息：<br />\n<br />\nInstagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hk_nationalist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhk_nationalist%2F&d=iXPG7n%2BZlQYRPUdsVi1iJozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=13f06fd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hk_nationalist/</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/2R0P6e8h4chsuJw?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F2R0P6e8h4chsuJw%3Fs%3D09&d=iXPG7n%2BZlQYRPUdsVi1iJozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b7208ad5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/2R0P6e8h4chsuJw?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKNFChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKNFChannel&d=iXPG7n%2BZlQYRPUdsVi1iJozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e185f0fa\" 